landing.heroDescription: Kuusaa beekumsa keessaa bal'aa ta'e battalumatti argadhu. Deeggartoota haala bu'a qabeessa fi gahumsaan gargaaruuf deebii sirrii fi madda qaban argadhu.

instantAnswers.title: Deebii Battalumaa
instantAnswers.description: Kuusaa beekumsa bal'aa keetii irraa deebii battalumaa madda waabii wajjin argadhu.

policyGuidance.title: Qajeelfama Imaammata
policyGuidance.description: Imaammata, adeemsa, fi qajeelfama deeggarsa maamilaa haaraa ta'e argadhu.

teamEfficiency.title: Bu'a Qabeessummaa Garee
teamEfficiency.description: Tajaajila maamiltootaa fooyya'aa ta'eef odeeffannoo walsimannaa fi sirrii ta'e garee kee hummeessi.
